text: Mohammad Naji Abdulrahman Abo Ayed (, born 30 October 1993) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Pro League side Al-Fateh. ==Career== Mohammad Naji he started his career of Redhoa in Saudi Third Division. On 19 July 2016, Mohammad Naji left Redhoa and joined Ohod. On 19 August 2018, Mohammad Naji left Ohod and joined Al-Jeel .
